<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Johann von Wittelsbach, Herzog von Pfalz-Neumarkt</head><p>Der Rat teilt wegen Pankraz von Puchberg mit, dass man Gulden alter Stadtwährung zu Nürnberg kaufen kann, und übermittelt die Wechselkurse.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_351" id="174v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_351_r1l9">Hercʒog Johanſen von Peyern </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab facs="#facs_351_r1l10"><expan>Gneͣdıg<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> / als vns eẅr
                            <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan>
<expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> hat / von des handels </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_351_r1l11"><expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> der becʒalung der
                                <expan>alte<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>Reyniſche<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>guld<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan>
<expan>ſtatweru<ex>n</ex>g</expan>
</ab>
<ab facs="#facs_351_r1l12">dıe Pangracʒ <expan>Puchperg<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>eine<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan> tun ſülle . Darauf eẅr </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_351_r1l13">gnade eins vnterſchaıds von vns begert
                                <expan>ʒuu<ex>er</ex>ſchreıben</expan> etc das </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_351_r1l14">haben wır wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> / Vnd
                        tun <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>fürſtenl<ex>ichen</ex></expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> ʒu wıſſen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_351_r1l15">daʒ wır ein <expan>Statweru<ex>n</ex>g</expan>
<expan>guld<ex>en</ex></expan> bey vns herbracht
                            <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> / <expan>derſelbe<ex>n</ex></expan>
</ab>
<ab facs="#facs_351_r1l16">
<add><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan></add>
<expan>ſtatweru<ex>n</ex>g</expan>
<expan>guld<ex>en</ex></expan> man bey vns wol ʒu kawffen fınde der es </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_351_r1l17">
<add><expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan></add> tun wölt / Wıe
                            <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> . ſo <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> wır
                        vns <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> ʒu eren </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_351_r1l18">erfaren / Daʒ dıe wechſler bey vns
                                <expan>derſ<ex>elben</ex></expan>
<expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan> ſtatwerung </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_351_r1l20"><expan>guld<ex>en</ex></expan> ye einen auf dıſʒ ʒeıt
                                <add><ab facs="#facs_351_r1l19">eın </ab></add> kawffen vmb
                                <expan>ein<ex>en</ex></expan> ſlechten
                            <expan>Reyniſche<ex>n</ex></expan>
</ab>
<ab facs="#facs_351_r1l21"><expan>guld<ex>en</ex></expan> / vnd vmb ij
                                <expan>groſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> vnd ȷ
                                <expan>d<ex>e</ex>n<ex>ario</ex></expan> vnd geben auf dıſʒ ʒeıt
                                <expan>derſ<ex>elben</ex></expan>
</ab>
<ab facs="#facs_351_r1l22"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan>
<expan>ſtatweru<ex>n</ex>g</expan>
<expan>guld<ex>en</ex></expan> ye einen <expan>wıd<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>awſʒ</expan> der ſıe von Jn
                            <expan>kawffe<ex>n</ex></expan>
</ab>
<ab facs="#facs_351_r1l23">wıl vmb ȷ <expan>ſlechte<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>Reyniſche<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>guld<ex>en</ex></expan> vnd vmb ij <expan>groſſ<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        vnd ij <expan>d<ex>e</ex>n<ex>ariis</ex></expan>
</ab>
<ab facs="#facs_351_r1l24"><expan>derſ<ex>elben</ex></expan>
<expan>d<ex>e</ex>n<ex>ariis</ex></expan> vij /
                            <expan>eın<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>groſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> bey vns gelten / Denn wo wır
                                <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan>
</ab>
<ab facs="#facs_351_r1l26"><expan>Hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> dıenſt vnd
                        wolgefallen etc </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_351_r1l27"><expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ıa</expan> vȷ<hi rend="sup">a</hi>
<expan>p<ex>oſt</ex></expan> martınj </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_351" id="174v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Herczog Johansen von Peyern</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Gneͣdig<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, als uns ewr
                            <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan>
<expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> hat von des handels
                                <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> der beczalung der
                                <expan>alte<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>reynische<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>guld<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan>
<expan>statweru<ex>n</ex>g</expan>, die Pangracz
                            <expan>Puchperg<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>eine<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan> tun sülle, darauf ewr gnade eins unterschaids
                        von uns begert <expan>zu v<ex>er</ex>schreiben</expan> etc., das haben wir
                        wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> und tun <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>fürstenl<ex>ichen</ex></expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> zu wissen, daz wir ein
                                <expan>statweru<ex>n</ex>g</expan>
<expan>guld<ex>en</ex></expan> bey uns herbracht
                            <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan>, <expan>derselbe<ex>n</ex></expan>
<add><expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan></add>
<expan>statweru<ex>n</ex>g</expan>
<expan>guld<ex>en</ex></expan> man bey uns wol zu kawffen finde, der es
                                    <add><expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan></add> tun wölt. Wie
                                <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> so <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> wir
                        uns <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> zu eren erfaren, daz die wechsler bey uns
                                <expan>ders<ex>elben</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan> statwerung <expan>guld<ex>en</ex></expan> ye
                        einen auf disz zeit <add>ein</add> kawffen umb <expan>ein<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        slechten <expan>reynische<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>guld<ex>en</ex></expan> und umb ii <expan>gross<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        und i <expan>d<ex>e</ex>n<ex>ario</ex></expan>; und geben auf disz zeit
                                <expan>ders<ex>elben</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan>
<expan>statweru<ex>n</ex>g</expan>
<expan>guld<ex>en</ex></expan> ye einen <expan>wid<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>awsz</expan>, der sie von in
                            <expan>kawffe<ex>n</ex></expan> wil, umb i
                            <expan>slechte<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>reynische<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>guld<ex>en</ex></expan> und umb ii <expan>gross<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        und ii <expan>d<ex>e</ex>n<ex>ariis</ex></expan>;
                            <expan>ders<ex>elben</ex></expan>
<expan>d<ex>e</ex>n<ex>ariis</ex></expan> vii <expan>ein<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>gross<ex>en</ex></expan> bey uns gelten. Denn wo wir
                                <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> dienst und wolgefallen etc.
                                <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> vi<hi rend="sup">a</hi>
<expan>p<ex>ost</ex></expan> Martini.</ab>
</div>
